The paper proposes a probabilistic-based classifier for binary classification problems, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The proposed classifier is evaluated on several datasets, including image classification datasets (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the benefits of probabilistic-driven classification techniques, which is related to data mining (cs.DM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
